<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n05006a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05006a">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05006a"> 6(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> who holds crozier / = bishop</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">So great was the veneration in which it <font color="green">[St. Patrick&apos;s <mark>crozier</mark>]</font> was held, says St. Bernard, that <mark>whoever possessed it</mark> was regarded by the simple and foolish populace as the <mark>true Bishop</mark>. <small> William Bullen Morris, <a name="WBML" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WBML"><cite title="source">The Life of Saint Patrick Apostle of Ireland</cite></a>, 4th ed. (1890) 200n</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
